# Feature-Based Architecture

This repository follows a Feature-Based Code Organization.

## Core Principle

Organize code by business capability (feature) rather than by technical layer.

A feature should contain everything required for its implementation:

* UI
* Domain logic
* Services
* Models
* Persistence
* Tests
* Documentation

